<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-1164] Make ARFF integration generate meta-data in JSON format</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1164</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a command line option to generate meta-data in a JSON format.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket supports the larger goal of making RF classifiers consume the meta-data and sequence files generated by the integration components.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1163&quot; title=&quot;Make random forest classifier meta-data file human readable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-1163&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-1163&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; makes RF classifiers read JSON meta-data.  This ticket is to get the ARFF integration to generate the same JSON formatted meta-data.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
